text: Bakhchisaray () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilchimbetovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 8 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Tuymazy, 16 km from Ilchimbetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Bakhchisaray, Republic of Bashkortostan
